Zeph: "That reframes everything. Consciousness as a moving target, defined by what we DON'T understand yet rather than what we do. In 1625, unexplained speech and reasoning meant soul/consciousness. In 2025, we've mechanically explained those, so consciousness retreats to biological substrate."
